.\"query various driver config settings
.DT
get_config
$MUDNAME$ driver help
get_config

.SH Name
.SI 5
get_config() - query various driver config settings
.EI

.SH Synopsis
.SI 5
mixed get_config( int );
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This efun is used to query the drivers various config settings.  Please
refer to the <runtime_config.h> include file for a list of currently
recognized options.
.EP

